  "description": "The thoughtful design of the refrigerator has a convenient storage of any products. This model is equipped with a CrispZone container, which makes it possible to significantly extend the shelf life of many fruits and vegetables that spoil quickly under standard conditions. The freezing zone is completed with the SpaceBox container. This is a special box that allows you to store much more than usual. It holds up to 38 liters. Refrigerator Gorenje NRK 6201 PW4 received a modern heat removal system. MultiFlow 360° technology makes the cooling screen more efficient than ever. Now the cold is distributed over the working compartments very quickly and extremely evenly. This refrigerator is efficient. This model is able to carry out high-quality freezing up to 12 kg of products per day. The operation of the refrigerator can be switched to holiday mode. This function allows you to keep the cold in the working chambers with minimal energy consumption. The model is equipped with handles with a hidden design. Hidden handles make the refrigerator look more modern. The refrigeration unit has a total volume of 331 liters, which will be enough to store food.",
